1
00:00:09,469 --> 00:00:10,845
When are you going on your next trip?
你下一次出差是什么时候?

2
00:00:11,420 --> 00:00:13,786
Pretty soon.It'll be to the Czech Republic.
快了. 是去捷克共和国(Czech Republic).

3
00:00:14,039 --> 00:00:16,798
Oh,I'm dying to go to Central Europe.
Oh, 我太想去中欧(Central Europe)了.

4
00:00:17,213 --> 00:00:18,195
I'm looking forward to it,
我盼着这次旅行快点儿到来,

5
00:00:18,496 --> 00:00:19,812
but it will be so much work.
但会有许多工作要做.

6
00:00:20,604 --> 00:00:21,038
Why?
为什么?

7
00:00:21,586 --> 00:00:27,487
Jim Bigelow wants the company's hotel in Prague to develope marketing plan just like ours.
Jim Bigelow想要公司在Prague的饭店制定出一个和我们一样的市场营销计划.

8
00:00:27,871 --> 00:00:28,606
Wow,great!
Wow, 太棒了!

9
00:00:29,181 --> 00:00:29,912
In three months.
要在三个月内完成.

10
00:00:31,242 --> 00:00:32,495
That is a lot of work.
那有好多工作要做.

11
00:00:32,934 --> 00:00:34,388
Anne,if I can do anything to help,
Anne, 要是我能帮上什么忙,

12
00:00:34,772 --> 00:00:35,370
please let me know.
请让我知道.

13
00:00:35,964 --> 00:00:36,273
I will.
我会的.

14
00:00:36,771 --> 00:00:38,775
And next time,take me with you.
下一次带我一起去,

15
00:00:40,224 --> 00:00:43,626
I want to sit in a cafe in the Old Town Square.
我想到Old Town Square的咖啡馆里坐坐.

16
00:00:43,964 --> 00:00:45,775
That is my favorite thing to do.
那也是我最喜欢做的事.

17
00:00:46,469 --> 00:00:48,087
And I hear there's great jazz.
我听说那儿的爵士乐很棒.

18
00:00:48,523 --> 00:00:48,777
Oh yes.
Oh yes.

19
00:00:49,147 --> 00:00:51,829
And serious shopping.Crystal...
也是购物的好地方.水晶…

20
00:00:52,103 --> 00:00:53,996
I'll pick some up for you,if you like.
我会帮你买一些, 如果你喜欢.

21
00:00:54,731 --> 00:00:56,999
Antique glass...Embroidery...
古董玻璃器(Antique glass...)...刺绣(Embroidery)...

22
00:00:57,843 --> 00:01:00,265
I've seen lovely china from there.
我还看过很漂亮的瓷器, 来自那边.

23
00:01:00,877 --> 00:01:04,002
Nina,it'll be much easier if you just come along.
Nina, 要不你和我一起去吧,那样事情就简单多了.

